@fortetapas does European cooking like no other! The decor was modern European inspired, with murals and paintings that give it an intriguing and vibrant look. This was my first time trying European food and tapas, and I will 1000% be back!!!!

Featured Cocktails: 

🍹 Gypsy Milk
🧉 Forte Jack Ass
🍹 Tropical Rum Mojito
🍸 Bedroom Martini 

Featured Food:

🥖 Tutmanik
🥔 Potato Vareniki
🧀 Charcuterie & Cheese Board
🥗 Burrata & Prosciutto Salad
🍕 Chicken Kabab with Plov
🥩 Lamb Chop Lollipop
🍤 Shrimp Empanadas with Chimichurri 
🍰 Biscuits Cake
🥞 Honey Walnut Crepe
🍏 Apple Strudel

We are excited to be a part of Las Vegas Restaurant Week!
While Las Vegas is a world-class culinary destination, many residents struggle with hunger. We are offering a special menu and a portion of the proceeds raised in Restaurant Week will help Three Square Food Bank continue to provide food to the community.

Please make your reservation at www.barforte.com we look forward to seeing you!
